{"tid":2002363,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"香港再出發究竟要出發去邊？","createTime":"2020-05-05T06:55:59.000Z","updateTime":"2020-05-05T08:29:13.000Z","uid":77036,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":31,"replies":[{"pid":"fd906b16c5ce00fc1e812f9b020e3b693e1aacc7","tid":2002363,"uid":77036,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:55:59.000Z","msg":"成班商人扯皮條咁多年嚟不停出賣香港將香港同支那同化<br />\n好似不斷逼個良家婦女出賣肉體流落風塵咁<br />\n好啦以家支那上面唔駛你班中間人白手套<br />\n親自落場啦直接操控香港啦<br />\n求仁得仁啦你班友都係想香港變支那姐<br />\n好啦而家又唔滿意又話要出發<br />\n而家香港法治經濟社會咪一早出發，呀唔係，係直情到左佢哋心目中嘅烏托幫支那囉<br />\n仲出發去邊撚度呀？吓？出發去美國呀？"},{"pid":"14639bc27df3affa164deba2fe0542b13b635225","tid":2002363,"uid":213877,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:56:49.000Z","msg":"出發上支那"},{"pid":"34eec650d71d499503ccf3aa2dd1c4f40c2b8727","tid":2002363,"uid":228955,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:57:07.000Z","msg":"Die ...."},{"pid":"57f5b16af88e871cc275b9ee007c28a3fc7199a8","tid":2002363,"uid":46388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:57:38.000Z","msg":"叫蟻民再出發令佢地有更多油水"},{"pid":"91082fdade86bccc2e380c9b5d9a9043fe832ab1","tid":2002363,"uid":23635,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:58:11.000Z","msg":"出發去地府<img src=\"/assets/faces/pig/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"fb3ab1b1bd7653394187846dc174ff62d70bd54e","tid":2002363,"uid":44171,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:58:29.000Z","msg":"滅亡"},{"pid":"e67b946de867157c12879a1f8b3ea753a059371f","tid":2002363,"uid":77036,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"57f5b16af88e871cc275b9ee007c28a3fc7199a8","tid":2002363,"uid":46388,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:57:38.000Z","msg":"叫蟻民再出發令佢地有更多油水"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-05-05T06:59:01.000Z","msg":"我都係咁諗<br />\n狡兔死走狗烹<br />\n成班人遲早俾支那共佢產<br />\n而家驚先死出嚟核撚突"},{"pid":"ff5d3dfd177ed82cefbc7b41772c4d124f224331","tid":2002363,"